comments.body: Really? Can A. millefolium have yellow blossoms? I thought only white or pink for that species.
I think in the wild it doesn't really come in yellow - but there are cultivated A. millefolium that are yellow.  At least, I have seen them labeled as A. millefolium at nurseries...
